[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "myst-batch"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "myst-batch"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["kvfi <mail@ouafi.net>"]
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
chrono = "0.4.19"
error-chain = "0.12.4"
job_scheduler = "1.2.1"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
lettre = "0.10"
log = "0.4.14"
serde_json = "1.0"
simple_logger = "4.0.0"
tera = "1"

[dependencies.diesel]
version = "2.0.2"
features = ["sqlite"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.3"
features = ["blocking", "json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]
